{"tid":1394129,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[電莖閪]我宣佈電莖其實喺維穩野","createTime":"2019-08-01T10:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:12:41.000Z","uid":116859,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"485c427094a6404a1dd4ae3842c3eccf92be9333","tid":1394129,"uid":116859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"雖然香港近排每日都有好多事發生，但生活都喺要過，作為一個愛國愛黨嘅電莖撚，由15年開始所有大大小小嘅活動都有去，當然咁多活動都肯定有好有壞，而作為每年最大型嘅音莖節，肯定仆住入場啦，開始之前不如比大家睇下去年嘅盛況先啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔想睇哂就碌到最底睇懶人包！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FromTheOtherWorld/videos/1920635231564525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFromTheOtherWorld%2Fvideos%2F1920635231564525%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=3412467d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FromTheOtherWorld/videos/1920635231564525/</a><br />\n<br />\n上年同電腦節夾住做效果唔喺咁好，今年一於夾住動漫做，肯定可以扳回頹勢，不過明眼人都見到喺動漫節嘅人上哂去玩，50蚊一張飛仲可以玩哂咁多野梗喺正啦喂，雖然另一方面又引起哂啲coser不滿，呢個又喺後話啦。到底點解政府每年都用咁大筆錢去搞音莖節呢？我地先由搞音莖節嘅公司講起，有留意電莖嘅朋友都知道每年音莖節都喺一間叫CGA嘅公司搞，啫喺<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">麥花臣林奠有去開幕果間公司。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sz72oNR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsz72oNR.png&h=0f8e6e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCGA有三位老闆，上圖分別喺周啟康同埋李嘉俊，仲有個無喺圖入面嘅老闆叫尹世豪，佢地都喺好早開始就搞緊電莖嘅有心人，亦成功令自己業務越嚟越大，仲創辦左一個香港電莖總會，之前亞運或者其他數碼港活動都好常見到佢哋個名，我地可以睇下協會架構先。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjshW75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjshW75.png&h=8cc558f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果喺IT狗應該成日見到佢哋會長個名，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">楊全盛喺其中一個資訊科技界別嘅建制派，同時香港智慧城市聯盟召集人兼創辦人</span></strong>，就喺點解我講電莖其實喺維穩野嘅重點。<br />\n<br />\n政府呢幾年一直都大力推動電莖發展，無論喺財政預算案定真正有撥款落去搞音莖節，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明顯比以前好多唔同新興行業有更多優待</span></strong>，仲就住場地牌照有豁免申請嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞網 - 電競場地領牌指引公布<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/04/20190408/20190408_160533_354.html?type=ticker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019%2F04%2F20190408%2F20190408_160533_354.html%3Ftype%3Dticker&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=fca8f8e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/04/20190408/20190408_160533_354.html?type=ticker</a><br />\n<br />\n另一方面政府就落左1億撥款落數碼港，希望佢哋喺商場入面建立一個比賽場地，依家數碼港中庭有個黑色大幕就喺其中一個數碼港成立嘅電莖場地，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而楊全盛正正喺今年三月底比政府委任成為數碼港董事。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立選落敗 建制「IT 紅人」 楊全盛 獲政府委任數碼港董事<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%B8%E8%90%BD%E6%95%97-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6-it-%E7%B4%85%E4%BA%BA-%E6%A5%8A%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%9B-%E7%8D%B2%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E6%B8%AF%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%2595%2597-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6-it-%25E7%25B4%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%259B%259B-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2591%25A3%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=3d337958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%2595%2597-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6-it-%25E7%25B4%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%259B%259B-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2591%25A3%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&h=a160ebbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%B8%E8%90%BD%E6%95%97-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6-it-%E7%B4%85%E4%BA%BA-%E6%A5%8A%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%9B-%E7%8D%B2%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E6%B8%AF%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n事實上數碼港好早就話要起電競場地，但個工程搞左半年都無消息，仲比蘋果質疑點解舊年4月公佈之後去到10月仲圍緊木板，但自從楊全盛做左數碼港董事之後，好似開左綠燈咁變魔術變哂所有野出嚟，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢個場地亦聲稱用左5000萬整出嚟</strong></span>，大家可以睇下圖覺得值唔值。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【施政報告】數碼港電競大樓木板圍封 進度成疑<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181010/58778004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778004&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=78288b36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778004&h=f9f67d8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181010/58778004</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DhCqmA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDhCqmA2.jpg&h=0b12e1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然講用左5000萬喺整場地，仲有5000萬又去左邊呢？就喺拎左去搞活動，而音莖節其中有part就叫「數碼港網絡紅人對抗賽」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢筆活動嘅錢如無意外都喺比左CGA搞</span></strong>。啱啱都提過CGA創辦左香港電競總會，楊全盛就喺入面嘅會長，就算無直接關係，都明顯有利益輸送嫌疑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3cBtf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3cBtf8.jpg&h=67df3ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上CGA同楊全盛唔喺第一次合作，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩年前CGA一早創立左第一間電莖館叫Versus Stadium，由楊全盛自己間天旭科技投資集團出錢</strong></span>，大家只要上一上佢哋個網同埋望下Versus Stadium下面個logo喺by CGA就知道兩者一直都有關鍵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.skyzervc.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skyzervc.com%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=d17dbc0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.skyzervc.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VSStadium/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FVSStadium%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=d6f1b7d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/VSStadium/</a><br />\n<br />\n不過有樣仲未fact check到，舊年5月CGA其實有將佢地公司28.57%股份轉售左比一間叫天時軟件有限公司，呢份公開文件亦有講到CGA呢幾年嘅財務狀況，16年同18年CGA都喺蝕緊錢，而17年喺唯一一年賺到錢，咁2017年又有咩事發生呢？正正就喺第一年搞音莖節，當中有無咩關係大家可以自己諗下。最終CGA規模亦都越滾越大，有咩人做生意喺蝕住做？除左連登仔搞船p之外我都諗唔到，所以天時軟件同楊全盛當中有無關係都好可疑，楊全盛亦都唔喺第一次發生呢啲事，2015年果陣都比人揭發過以公帑補貼私人生意，呢部份睇下有無咩巴絲釐清。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.timeless.com.hk/b5/attachment/announcements/c-Timeless-CGA-final.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeless.com.hk%2Fb5%2Fattachment%2Fannouncements%2Fc-Timeless-CGA-final.pdf&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=fe02a14a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.timeless.com.hk/b5/attachment/announcements/c-Timeless-CGA-final.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n最後講多樣關於唔關電莖嘅野事，啱啱都有提過楊全盛喺香港智慧城市聯盟召集人兼創辦人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所謂智慧城市到底喺乜野？其中一個最重要嘅議題就喺大家近排成日講嘅智能燈柱</strong></span>，睇返政府今年4月嘅報告，智能燈柱正正就喺其中一個好重要嘅部份，之後嘅野有更多post可以搵嚟睇，亦證明到楊全盛都喺智能燈柱其中一位推手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tR2eeWO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtR2eeWO.jpg&h=c77aab97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會 - 發展智慧城市的最新情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ogcio.gov.hk/tc/news/legco_papers/2019/04/doc/lb_20190416.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ogcio.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Flegco_papers%2F2019%2F04%2Fdoc%2Flb_20190416.pdf&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=62a74dfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ogcio.gov.hk/tc/news/legco_papers/2019/04/doc/lb_20190416.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n所以大家喺到支持緊電莖嘅同時，其實都喺幫緊建制維穩，義士喺外面打生打死你哋就涼住冷氣，連軍師都算唔上幫政府維穩咋。<br />\n<br />\n利申：愛國愛黨，最鍾意去電莖活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懶人包：<br />\n1. 記住8月5號去罷工<br />\n2. 所有電莖撥款都喺維穩費<br />\n3. 所有野都只喺利益輸送<br />\n4. 楊全盛喺智能燈柱推手<br />\n5. CGA + 楊全盛 + Cyberport = 政府電莖 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f73061dd1cc86a864d8757befdec16382a546500","tid":1394129,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"奧運會都係宣揚和平理性非暴力"},{"pid":"6aa3a70aa9547c47e8ea03de9071d1bc1211d05f","tid":1394129,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"達狗fans話政府推電莖業 對香港電莖好wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hj9TvQ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhj9TvQ0.png&h=f95fc005&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f4f7b8f809bf5c04b8731fa21de0db8028032bb","tid":1394129,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"本身電競就係幫廢青揾最後一口飯食，不過商業味太濃做就一班正常人食左廢青最後逃生門"},{"pid":"9eead6974ce65c1de1c7a28fd410b72185d4c3eb","tid":1394129,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc5a76dc5c3de61309657f8166882a976a3bed29","tid":1394129,"uid":145292,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"係呃班後生仔打電競，唔理社會"},{"pid":"85843fa7310e6737f2299650ac3c092eb55dea1c","tid":1394129,"uid":10150,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:13:04.000Z","msg":"但間野8 月5 全公司罷工 關門wo"},{"pid":"1dc1376280edcf500cf0543314e2f66442ab8cf0","tid":1394129,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike